These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
City: hamburg, miami, venice, hannover
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, apricot, pink, orange
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, fonseca, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, june, august
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, zinnia, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, spy, action, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person who likes light-blue is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who growstulip##2
 2. the person who likes pink is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person driving the bus and the person who growsaconite##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes orange is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes apricot##1
11. the person watching horror movies is the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
13. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
14. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
15. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| City      | venice        | hannover     | miami | hamburg      |
| Color          | pink | apricot    | light-blue      | orange  |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | baccarat    | montecristo       | fonseca     |
| Birthday   | june        | august       | july          | april |
| Flower           | zinnia    | tulip | marigold      | aconite     |
| Movie-Genre         | crime   | spy   | action      | horror    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

